  "title": "Human Resource Executive (HR Exec)",
  "description": "<p>People are the heartbeat of an organisation. You have the chance to be part of the team that keeps the heartbeat going strong! So, do you have what it takes to keep Beacon's heart pumping?</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Recruitment and Talent Retention</strong></u><strong>: </strong>Are you able to spot that talent from the sea of applications? Have you successfully implemented ideas that retain star performers?</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Onboarding and Talent Development</strong></u><strong>:</strong> Do you know how to assimilate new joiners into the new environment? Can you transform \"raw talents\" into \"shining stars\"?</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Performance Management</strong></u><strong>: </strong>Have you played a key role in the performance management process?</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Employee Engagement</strong></u><strong>: </strong>Have you run programmes / initiatives to ensure employees stay engaged and motivated, and ultimately stay with the organisation?</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Corporate Social Responsibility</strong></u><strong>: </strong>Do you believe in giving back to the community (environment, people and commercial)?</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>If the above describes you perfectly, we want you!</p>\n<p><br></p>",
